data.description: Welcome home to this remarkable property! Modern living meets eco-friendliness with solar panels and a Type 2 EV charger. Revel in comfort with central A/C and entertain under the pergola overlooking Asian Pear and Cherry trees. A 2017 full remodel ensures contemporary style, while a 7-year-old roof provides peace of mind. Nestled in a great neighborhood, this home is more than a residence; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously cared-for property yours – where every detail, from energy efficiency to outdoor charm, enhances your living experience. Act now and embrace a home that embodies comfort, convenience, and community!
